; Coverage test for post.cc lookup switch branches.
; Exercises multiple lookup paths: 'i' case for index (L460-462),
; 'm' case for magnitude (L464-467), 'u' case for use_direct_amount
; (L499-502), 'v' case for virtual and value_date (L504-509),
; 'x' case for xact and xact_id (L511-516).
; Also covers checkin/checkout NULL returns (L348-352).

2024/01/01 (CODE1) * Grocery
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Gas
    (Budget:Gas)     $30.00
    Expenses:Gas     $30.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(index)|%(magnitude)|%(value_date)|%(xact_id)|%(account)\n"
1|$10.00|2024/01/01|1|Expenses:Food
2|$10.00|2024/01/01|2|Assets:Cash
3|$60.00|2024/01/02|1|Budget:Gas
4|$60.00|2024/01/02|2|Expenses:Gas
5|$60.00|2024/01/02|3|Assets:Cash
end test
